* sample design
* KEEP hotels in Vienna, stars 3 to 4
* DROP observation with erroneous price variable (price>1000)
keep if accommodation_type== "Hotel"
keep if stars>=3 & stars<=4
keep if price<1000

* brief look at data
tab city
tab stars

